friend had one years ago  that had a round foot that fit the end of the
crankshaft and claws that  used the stock holes in the pulley. It was
very low profile, looked like it  was designed for VWs only. I have not
seen one like it since. This is for  another friends Bug, or I would just
pull the tin. Any help would be  appreciated. Thanks, Timo



hello Timo  Empi and bug pack sell those. In a pinch you can take a  long 
